This is the experiment done for to find out if it's possible to Use Ngram Models and Statics to actually Identify the South African Languages. 
The work done is based on the paper N-Gram-Based Text Categorization by William B. Cavnar and John M. Trenkle.
The actuall implementation will be added soon after the results are computed and it is deemed possible to do perform Identification at an acceptable Accuracy  rate
